---
// index.astro
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>BORJA MOSKV // NO SLEEP IN MY CITY</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Audio directo, vídeo en primer plano, ciudad al fondo." />
    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;600;800;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      :root {
        --color-bg: #0A0A0A;
        --color-text: #F3F4F6;
        --color-accent: #2B3BE5;
        --font-sans: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
        --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      }
      
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
        scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
      }

      body {
        background-color: var(--color-bg);
        color: var(--color-text);
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        min-height: 100vh;
        width: 100vw;
        position: relative;
        overflow-y: auto;
        overflow-x: hidden;
      }

      /* Background Video */
      .bg-video-container {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        z-index: 0;
      }
      
      .bg-video {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        opacity: 0.6; /* Slight dimming to make text readable */
      }

      /* Overlay Gradient */
      .overlay {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(10,10,10,0.1) 0%, rgba(10,10,10,0.85) 100%);
        z-index: 1;
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      /* Navigation */
      .top-nav {
        position: fixed;
        top: 3rem;
        right: 4rem;
        z-index: 100;
        display: flex;
        gap: 3rem;
      }

      .nav-link {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .nav-link:hover {
        color: #FFFFFF;
      }

      /* Viewport Wrapper for Snap Scroll */
      .hero-viewport {
        height: 100vh;
        width: 100%;
        position: relative;
        scroll-snap-align: start;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      /* Giant Title */
      .hero-title {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        z-index: 10;
        font-size: 16vw;
        font-weight: 900;
        white-space: nowrap;
        color: transparent;
        -webkit-text-stroke: 2px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        pointer-events: none;
        user-select: none;
        line-height: 1;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      /* Bottom Left Info */
      .track-info {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 3rem;
        left: 4rem;
        z-index: 10;
        display: flex;
        gap: 4rem;
      }

      .info-group {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        position: relative;
      }

      .info-group:not(:last-child)::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        right: -2rem;
        top: 15%;
        height: 70%;
        width: 1px;
        background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      }

      .info-label {
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      }

      .info-value {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      }

      /* Bottom Right Actions */
      .action-buttons {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 3rem;
        right: 4rem;
        z-index: 10;
        display: flex;
        gap: 2.5rem;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .action-btn {
        background: none;
        border: none;
        color: var(--color-text);
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        cursor: pointer;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        text-decoration: none;
        opacity: 0.8;
      }

      .action-btn:hover {
        opacity: 1;
      }

      .action-btn.primary {
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 100px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        opacity: 1;
      }

      .action-btn.primary:hover {
        border-color: var(--color-text);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      }
      
      .arrow-icon {
        width: 16px;
        height: 16px;
        fill: none;
        stroke: currentColor;
        stroke-width: 1.5;
        stroke-linecap: square;
      }

      /* Blog Section */
      .blog-section {
        scroll-snap-align: start;
        min-height: 100vh;
        width: 100%;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
        background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.85);
        backdrop-filter: blur(35px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(35px);
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 8rem 4rem 4rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .blog-section-header {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto 4rem;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: baseline;
      }

      .blog-section-title {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
      }

      .blog-section-title span {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF0055, #2B3BE5);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
      }

      .blog-section-subtitle {
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .blog-grid {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      .blog-card-inline {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        min-height: 320px;
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .blog-card-inline::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 2px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #FF0055, #2B3BE5, transparent);
        transform: scaleX(0);
        transition: transform 0.4s ease;
      }

      .blog-card-inline:hover {
        transform: translateY(-6px);
        border-color: rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.3);
        background: rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.03);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), 0 0 25px rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.05);
      }

      .blog-card-inline:hover::before {
        transform: scaleX(1);
      }

      .card-meta {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .card-tag {
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 0.6rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #FF0055;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.25);
        padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
        border-radius: 100px;
      }

      .card-tag.tech {
        color: #2B3BE5;
        border-color: rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.25);
      }

      .card-date {
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      }

      .card-title {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.3;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #FFFFFF;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      }

      .card-excerpt {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        flex-grow: 1;
      }

      .card-cta {
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .blog-card-inline:hover .card-cta {
        color: #FFFFFF;
      }

      .blog-footer {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 4rem auto 0;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .view-all-btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        color: #FFFFFF;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .view-all-btn:hover {
        border-color: #2B3BE5;
        background: rgba(43, 59, 229, 0.08);
      }

      @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .blog-grid {
          grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .blog-section {
          padding: 6rem 2rem 2rem;
        }
        .blog-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        .top-nav {
          right: 2rem;
          gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        .track-info {
          left: 2rem;
          gap: 2rem;
        }
        .action-buttons {
          right: 2rem;
          gap: 1.5rem;
        }
      }

    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Background Layer -->
    <div class="bg-video-container">
      <video class="bg-video" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
        <source src="/media/videos/no-sleep-in-my-city.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
    </div>
    <div class="overlay"></div>

    <!-- UI Layer -->
    <header>
      <nav class="top-nav">
        <a href="#" class="nav-link">Música</a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-link">Vídeo</a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-link">Imagen</a>
        <a href="#blog" class="nav-link">Blog</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <!-- Hero Viewport -->
      <div class="hero-viewport">
        <h1 class="hero-title">BORJA MOSKV</h1>

        <div class="track-info">
          <div class="info-group">
            <span class="info-label">Obra</span>
            <span class="info-value">No Sleep In My City</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-group">
            <span class="info-label">Formato</span>
            <span class="info-value">Video musical</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-group">
            <span class="info-label">Duración</span>
            <span class="info-value">03:35</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-buttons">
          <a href="#" class="action-btn">
            Escuchar ahora
            <svg class="arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="action-btn">
            Ver la pieza
            <svg class="arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
          <button class="action-btn primary">
            Modo pieza
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Blog / Diario Section -->
      <section id="blog" class="blog-section">
        <div class="blog-section-header">
          <h2 class="blog-section-title"><span>Diario</span> / Transmisiones</h2>
          <span class="blog-section-subtitle">Industrial Noir Editorial</span>
        </div>

        <div class="blog-grid">
          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <a href="/blog/substack-mafia-autopsia-estructural" class="blog-card-inline">
            <div class="card-meta">
              <span class="card-tag">Investigación</span>
              <span class="card-date">2026.06.01</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="card-title">Substack Mafia: Autopsia Estructural</h3>
              <p class="card-excerpt">Análisis forense de la arquitectura comercial y validación algorítmica coordinada en un ecosistema privado.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="card-cta">
              Ver autopsia
              <svg class="arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </span>
          </a>

          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <a href="/blog/ultramap-substrate" class="blog-card-inline">
            <div class="card-meta">
              <span class="card-tag tech">Auditoría Silicio</span>
              <span class="card-date">2026.06.01</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="card-title">ULTRAMAP-Ω: Autopsia del Sustrato</h3>
              <p class="card-excerpt">Análisis de la memoria física lock-free y la orquestación del enjambre K-0 bajo la física del silicio.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="card-cta">
              Ver auditoría
              <svg class="arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </span>
          </a>

          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <a href="/blog/termodinamica-de-agentes" class="blog-card-inline">
            <div class="card-meta">
              <span class="card-tag">Ensayo</span>
              <span class="card-date">2026.03.25</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="card-title">Termodinámica de Agentes</h3>
              <p class="card-excerpt">La paradoja del cómputo: cuando el aumento de la inteligencia agéntica expande el desorden termodinámico.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="card-cta">
              Leer ensayo
              <svg class="arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="blog-footer">
          <a href="/blog" class="view-all-btn">
            Ver diario completo
            <svg class="arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
